{"tid":126323,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（保險狗) AIA上月向醫生發信列多項手術不賠住院費","createTime":"2017-02-19T09:03:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-19T12:11:52.000Z","uid":29314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a4eb2407fb13775331b7a8b0061fb2971e72fafa","tid":126323,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T09:03:02.000Z","msg":"友邦保險上月底突然向私家醫生發信指，公司已為提供住院賠償的「醫療所需」下定義，表明腸鏡、十二指腸胃鏡、白內障手術等，並非必須住院的醫療項目，建議醫生無須為病人安排住院。"},{"pid":"f8be527415ebe32088d8a3113df9e4dfbd346c99","tid":126323,"uid":70415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T09:04:15.000Z","msg":"唔係話自己好偉大架咩，成日同人講幫到人真係開心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5329ae1cfb1c4e3d65aa84adb158914a782ace5","tid":126323,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T09:04:34.000Z","msg":"提出所謂「醫療所需」概念，&hellip;&hellip;病人在進行某部份手術時，將不獲住院賠償。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n信中又特別舉例指，腸鏡、十二指腸胃鏡、白內障手術，<span style=\"color: red;\">即使要以監察麻醉下進行，任何住院費用也不獲賠償</span>。"},{"pid":"01cb9b8aa4a05a499bafe388b7ba23ef98369dea","tid":126323,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T09:05:23.000Z","msg":"幫到人自己又開心"},{"pid":"c11776145f0b58e082c0909b4d4856acd822ffa2","tid":126323,"uid":78785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T09:05:26.000Z","msg":"&quot;阿john 比車撞到...."},{"pid":"7990f22fd43c688c05ac103cbb7faf2df6479ef0","tid":126323,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T09:07:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"883a66f685ae39f45904b59e428c561052bc805d","tid":126323,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T09:09:42.000Z","msg":"可以幫到人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcac5ef49d01ab62685820ffd5b2f3911924a369","tid":126323,"uid":9899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T09:17:49.000Z","msg":"咁手術費賠唔賠"},{"pid":"c203